  "_comment": "Drop-in JSON-LD templates for CogniFit competitor comparison pages. Replace placeholders marked with {{ }}. Every page should include: (1) WebPage/Article, (2) Product for CogniFit, (3) FAQPage, and for roundups (4) ItemList. All ratings must cite verified sources. All pricing stamped with date. Schema is additive to the existing @graph on the landing page.",

